    <h1>4- Influencer data management SOP - Private Brands</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 id=3D"id-4-InfluencerdatamanagementSOP-PrivateBrands-Purposeand=
Scope">
<style>[data-colorid=3Dxm0jhrnhra]{color:#403294} html[data-color-mode=3Dda=
rk] [data-colorid=3Dxm0jhrnhra]{color:#796bcd}[data-colorid=3Dz8p4bdklan]{c=
olor:#403294} html[data-color-mode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dz8p4bdklan]{colo=
r:#796bcd}[data-colorid=3Dt6z2h0xqzi]{color:#403294} html[data-color-mode=
=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dt6z2h0xqzi]{color:#796bcd}[data-colorid=3Dghba5sk3=
ke]{color:#403294} html[data-color-mode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dghba5sk3ke]=
{color:#796bcd}</style><strong>Purpose and Scope</strong></h2>
<p>To align, manage and track influencer meets across distributor and retai=
ler locations, in order to educate and onboard potential partners and incre=
ase sales reach.</p>
<p><strong>Handover timeline: PB -&gt;BizOps: </strong><time datetime=3D"20=
25-09-08" class=3D"date-past">08 Sep 2025</time></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-4-InfluencerdatamanagementSOP-PrivateBrands-Stakeholders"><str=
ong>Stakeholders</strong></h2>
<p>Data sourcing - Sales</p>
<p>Sourcing channel - WhatsApp</p>
<p>Data management - BizOps</p>
<p>Data management platform - Excel</p>
<h2 id=3D"id-4-InfluencerdatamanagementSOP-PrivateBrands-Steps"><strong>Ste=
ps</strong></h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>For planned meets, Sales team to update primary details of influencer me=
ets planned in the <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://jsw-my.sharep=
oint.com/:x:/r/personal/kunal_jani_jsw_in/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=3D=
%7B83DF62F5-B42A-43F8-A626-0FB7948B4710%7D&amp;file=3DFY%2026%20Q2%20-%20ch=
annel%20growth%20plan.xlsx&amp;fromShare=3Dtrue&amp;action=3Ddefault&amp;mo=
bileredirect=3Dtrue" rel=3D"nofollow">Channel Growth Plan</a> sheet, fillin=
g in from column A-&gt;M as below:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Sr. No.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Account Sf ID of Dealer</p></li>
<li>
<p>Name of the Dealer</p></li>
<li>
<p>State</p></li>
<li>
<p>Zone</p></li>
<li>
<p>District</p></li>
<li>
<p>Distributor Name</p></li>
<li>
<p>Account Owner</p></li>
<li>
<p>Responsible KAM/SM/TM</p></li>
<li>
<p>Pin code</p></li>
<li>
<p>Onboarded Dealer Month</p></li>
<li>
<p>Type of Meet to be conducted</p></li>
<li>
<p>#Meet</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li>
<p>For unplanned meets, BizOps to fill the above details manually, referrin=
g to PB WA group- "JSW One PB tmt sales".</p></li>
<li>
<p>Sales team to update remarks from column N-&gt;Q, mentioning the meeting=
 status, remarks if not planned, and general remarks related to the meeting=
.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Post the sales team=E2=80=99s remarks, PB HO team user to update their r=
emarks in column R, updating status if the dealer in now registered, meetin=
g needs to be rescheduled, or other dealers need to be approached etc.</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p>Once a meet is successful, BizOps to record further details of actual me=
etings from S-&gt;W as required in the same sheet.</p></li>
<li>
<p>For meets that are successful, Sales team needs to capture the attendanc=
e and details of all attendees in the <em><span data-colorid=3D"ghba5sk3ke"=
>required format</span></em> on <em><span data-colorid=3D"z8p4bdklan">Whats=
App group </span></em><span data-colorid=3D"t6z2h0xqzi">'JSW One PB tmt sal=
es'</span><em><span data-colorid=3D"xm0jhrnhra">, </span></em>and share wit=
h the BizOps team, to be captured in a separate tracker- <a class=3D"extern=
al-link" href=3D"https://jsw-my.sharepoint.com/:x:/r/personal/supriya_shara=
n_jsw_in/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=3D%7BA64A80F3-5C53-4C99-975D-B9563C=
06DFBA%7D&amp;file=3DNew%20-%20Influencer%20Data%20Format.xlsx&amp;fromShar=
e=3Dtrue&amp;action=3Ddefault&amp;mobileredirect=3Dtrue" rel=3D"nofollow">I=
nfluencer meets data</a>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>BizOps to verify attendance vs attendees data shared by sales.</p></li>
<li>
<p>The above captured data to be pushed to Salesforce every month-end by Pr=
oduct team to be updated in the Customer Master, for Sales team=E2=80=99s f=
uture perusal.</p></li>
</ol>
<p><strong>TAT for data updation:</strong></p>
<p>24 hrs from details shared on WhatsApp</p>
